OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FIt has been 20 years since 23 Chinese
OL,7,Fcockle pickers drowned when they were
OL,8,Fcut off by the tide at
OL,10,FThe workers, all aged between 18 and
OL,11,F45, had been ordered out to the
OL,12,Ftideline after being trafficked into
OL,13,Fthe area by gangmasters to work.
OL,15,FThey spoke little English and had no
OL,16,Flocal knowledge or relevant skills,
OL,17,Fand were working to send money back to
OL,18,Ftheir families in China.
