OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FBut what happened on 5 February 2004?
OL,8,FWhat happened?
OL,10,FAt around 4pm on 5 February 2004
OL,11,Faround 30 workers set out to collect
OL,12,Fcockles from a stretch of Bay at low
OL,13,Ftide.
OL,15,FWhen they arrived, a group of local
OL,16,Fcockle pickers tried to warn them that
OL,17,Fthe tide would soon be coming in.
OL,19,FTrevor Fleming explained how he tried
OL,20,Fto speak to one Chinese cockle picker.
