OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FHe said: "The wind was picking up, and
OL,7,Fthat was going to bring the tide in a
OL,8,Flot quicker.
OL,10,F"We noticed Chinese workers walking
OL,11,Fonto the sand, and we just knew there
OL,12,Fwas no way they could walk out and
OL,13,Fwalk back in time.
OL,15,F"They didn't understand a word I was
OL,16,Fsaying. They just smiled at me... and
OL,17,Fwalked off into the dark that night."
