OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FThe workers relied on their boss, Lin
OL,7,FLiang Ren, to instruct them on when
OL,8,Fthey would have to stop working, but
OL,9,Fthose instructions never came.
OL,11,FLater that evening, a fast, sweeping
OL,12,Ftide cut off the pickers and left many
OL,13,Fof them stranded on sand-banks as the
OL,14,Fwater began to rise.
OL,16,FAccording to survivors, the cocklers
OL,17,Fwere never told what to do in an
OL,18,Femergency or even asked if they could
OL,19,Fswim.
