OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FWhen the tides began to come in, the
OL,7,Fworkers did not know how to get back
OL,8,Fto shore.
OL,10,FNine workers were trapped in their
OL,11,Fpickup truck, which they used to
OL,12,Ftraverse the mudflats, as the water
OL,13,Frose.
OL,15,FAll nine removed their waterproof
OL,16,Fclothing and swam for their lives, but
OL,17,Fonly four made it back to the shore.
OL,18,FThe other five swam in a different
OL,19,Fdirection and drowned.
