OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FAround 9:30pm one worker, Guo Bing
OL,7,FLong, called 999, using his limited
OL,8,FEnglish to tell emergency services:
OL,9,F"Sinking water, many many, sinking
OL,10,Fwater... Sinking water, sinking water."
OL,12,FMr Long also managed to phone his
OL,13,Ffamily, telling them he was trapped.
OL,15,FOther workers called their bosses for
OL,16,Fhelp. Lin Liang Ren's cousin, Lin Mu
OL,17,FYong, was on his way to the bay when
OL,18,Fhe learnt what had happened.
