OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FIt was his girlfriend, Janie Bannister
OL,7,Ffrom Liverpool, who called the
OL,8,Femergency services at 9.17pm for help.
OL,9,FTen minutes later, she called again to
OL,10,Fsay the water was still rising.
OL,12,FAn extensive search and rescue
OL,13,Foperation was launched by the
OL,14,FCoastguard, police, and ambulance
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FMorecambe's crew worked for 22 hours
OL,18,Fduring the rescue operation.
