OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FA total of 21 bodies - between the
OL,7,Fages of 18 and 45 - were recovered
OL,8,Fwithin hours, a woman's skull washed
OL,9,Fup six years later, and one man has
OL,10,Fnever been found.
OL,12,F15 more from the group managed to
OL,13,Fescape to safety.
OL,15,FMichael Guy, the lifeboat operations
OL,16,Fmanager was on duty that night. He
OL,17,Fsaid his crew were confronted with a
OL,18,F"sea of bodies."
