OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FThe workers were trafficked into
OL,7,FEngland through containers into
OL,8,FLiverpool. They were then hired out by
OL,9,Fagents of Chinese organised crime
OL,10,Fgangs - known as Triads.
OL,12,FThey were all illegal immigrants,
OL,13,Fmainly from the Fujian province of
OL,14,FChina.
OL,16,FAll had agreed to be brought to the UK
OL,17,Fin the belief they would be given the
OL,18,Fopportunity to work and send money
OL,19,Fback to their families, many of whom
OL,20,Fwere living in poverty.
