OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FAmong the dead was a married couple;
OL,7,FLiu Qin Ying and her husband Xu Yu Hua.
OL,9,FMost had been previously employed as
OL,10,Ffarmers, and two were fishermen.
OL,12,FAll the bodies were found between the
OL,13,Fcockling area and shore indicating
OL,14,Fmost had attempted to swim but had
OL,15,Fbeen overcome by hypothermia.
OL,17,FA survivor of the tragedy, who was
OL,18,Ffrom Liverpool, is now living under an
OL,19,Fassumed name under the care of the
OL,20,FGovernment's witness protection
OL,21,Fservice.
