OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FHave there been any prosecutions?
OL,8,FGangmaster Lin Liang Ren was jailed
OL,9,Ffor 14 years after being found guilty
OL,10,Fof manslaughter and facilitating
OL,11,Fillegal immigration.
OL,13,FHis trial heard he would drive the
OL,14,Fworkers to Morecambe from Liverpool
OL,15,Fand visit casinos while the men and
OL,16,Fwomen toiled through the night.
OL,18,FHe was deported back to China in
OL,19,FSeptember 2012 after serving two years
OL,20,Fon remand and a further six years in
OL,21,Fprison.
