OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FRen's girlfriend, Zhao Xiao Qing, and
OL,7,Fhis cousin, Lin Mu Yong, were also
OL,8,Fconvicted of assisting the cocklers to
OL,9,Fbreach immigration laws.
OL,11,FYong was sentenced to four years and
OL,12,Fnine months, while Qing to two years
OL,13,Fand nine months.
OL,15,FDavid Anthony Eden Sr. and David
OL,16,FAnthony Eden Jr., from Prenton,
OL,17,FMerseyside, who bought cockles from
OL,18,Fthe work gang, were cleared of helping
OL,19,Fthe workers break immigration law.
