OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FA year after the tragedy the
OL,7,FGangmasters Licensing Authority (GLA)
OL,8,Fwas created.
OL,10,FIt was designed to target rogue
OL,11,Fgangmasters and requires anyone
OL,12,Fsupplying workers into the shellfish
OL,13,Fsector, and across agriculture, and
OL,14,Fhorticulture to hold a licence with
OL,15,Fthe GLA.
OL,17,FMore than 16,000 licence applications
OL,18,Fwere approved between 2005-2022.
