OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FA total of 77 unlicensed gangmasters
OL,7,Fhave also been successfully prosecuted
OL,8,Fby the GLA across the UK between 2005
OL,9,Fand 2022.
OL,11,FIn 2017 the GLA became GLAA
OL,12,F(Gangmasters and Labour Abuse
OL,13,FAuthority), with additional
OL,14,Fresponsibilities to tackle labour
OL,15,Fexploitation across the economy, and
OL,16,Fto investigate modern slavery where it
OL,17,Frelates to labour abuse and other
OL,18,Foffences.
