OL,3,CWhat happened in the Morecambe Bay
OL,4,Ccockle picking disaster?
OL,6,FCommercial cocklers are now required
OL,7,Fto apply for a permit before they are
OL,8,Fallowed to work in Morecambe Bay.
OL,10,FThe tragedy also contributed to the
OL,11,Fintroduction of the Modern Slavery Act
OL,12,Fin 2015.
OL,14,FThe law set out more effective
OL,15,Fpunishment for traffickers and those
OL,16,Fforcing vulnerable people into illegal
OL,17,Fwork, as well as bringing in provision
OL,18,Ffor the protection of victims.
